page.title: 13 My Free Time
page.content:
My name is David Pickett and I have a sister called Lynda.I am 10 and she is 7.My dad works for Austin/Rover at the car factory and he drives an Austin Maestro.My mum does part-time cleaning work and she has a Leyland Mini.We all live in Latchford Lane in Gt Haseley. At weekends and after school I like playing on my bike around the village.I play at BMX with the other boys like Stephen and Brian. At night I use my computer and play games such as Harrier Jet,Hungry Horrace,Horrace goes Skiing,Maths games ,Football,Cricket and Atic Atac. I also like gardening.This year I grew a lot of cress and sold it around the village.
by David Pickett.
